MATCH path = (n0:Compound)<-[:`has-part_ChpC`]-(n1)-[:`drug-used-for-treatment_DduftC`]-(n2:Disease)
USING JOIN ON n1
WHERE n0.identifier = { source }
AND n2.identifier = { target }
AND n0 <> n1
WITH
[
size((n0)<-[:`has-part_ChpC`]-()),
size(()<-[:`has-part_ChpC`]-(n1)),
size((n1)-[:`drug-used-for-treatment_DduftC`]-()),
size(()-[:`drug-used-for-treatment_DduftC`]-(n2))
] AS degrees, path
RETURN
count(path) AS PC,
sum(reduce(pdp = 1.0, d in degrees| pdp * d ^ -{ w })) AS DWPC
